title: Gigabitcapable
extract: Gigabit LTE will give your current phone insane speeds. ... Gigabit LTE is capable of delivering speeds up to 1 Gbps. In the real world, this often translates to speeds around 400 Mbps, but compared to the national averages of 23 Mbps (for mobile networks) and 64 Mbps (at home), it is a substantial improvement.Dec 31, 2017
